{"tid":1527364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇年報，搵春袋","createTime":"2019-09-01T10:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T11:18:45.000Z","uid":46480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef4df4d18b0300885855d498b3d01b9c9e278fc","tid":1527364,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2019/0412/ltn201904129974_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2019%2F0412%2Fltn201904129974_c.pdf&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=1d923ba8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2019/0412/ltn201904129974_c.pdf</a><br />\n黨鐵2018年報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDERN1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDERN1.png&h=0da7b428&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZn2PzH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZn2PzH.png&h=4a17b931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢2018 利潤 16156M<br />\n香港客運業務收入19490M, 53.4M/day<br />\n車站商務收入 6458M, 17.7M/day<br />\n總計香港收入 25948M<br />\n大家唔幫趁港鐵商場<br />\n再加每日跳閘<br />\n只要令佢收入減6成， 25948M x 0.6 = 15568M<br />\n己經可以令黨鐵無錢搵<br />\n再努力啲去到7-8成就可以要佢倒蝕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上<a href=\"https://www.hkexnews.hk/index_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Findex_c.htm&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=2a2bc943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkexnews.hk/index_c.htm</a><br />\n所有上市公司年報都一定會有，有佢年報就可以對準春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2f5c7a98f99893a43cb1af8f546f5106190b65","tid":1527364